<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Consumer<sp/>(inside<sp/>a<sp/>protothread):</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
